quran[88]{c,v,t}:
  38,1,"Swaad. Jewe Allah, Ndarahiye kuri Qor’ani yibutsa abantu kwikebuka ku vyo bagosweko!"
  38,2,"Ariko rero, abagararije bagira amanyama mu guhonyanga ukuri bagaca kubiri na kwo."
  38,3,"Hari imigwi myinshi y’abantu Twahoneje hambere yabo, yatakamvye mu kwigaya igihe ishikirwa n’ibihano, ico gihe umwanya wo kwigaya wari wamaze kurengerana, nta n’ubukiriro yari igifise bwo guhunga nya bihano."
  38,4,"Abagarariji, baritangaje ku kurungikirwa Umugabisha avuye mu bantu nkabo, kugira abagabishe ku bihano vy’Imana Allah, yongere abararikire kuyemera, baraheza barinamura bati: “Uyu, ni umurozi karuhariwe mu kubesha;"
  38,5,"Karashize ingani, afate imana zacu azigire Imana Imwe Rudende, abe ari Yo aturarikira kwemera! Mu vy’ukuri, iryo rarikiramana ryiwe, ni ukuri ni ikintu gitangaje pe!”."
  38,6,"Indongozi z’abagararije zarahimirije abantu bazo gukomeza gutsimbatara mw’ibangikanyamana ziti: “Nimushishikare mutsimbatare mudahesha mu gusenga imana zanyu. Mu vy’ukuri inyigisho z’iyi Ntumwa, ni ukuri zifise ihangiro ryo kwiganza no kwigarurira ubutegetsi."
  38,7,"Kuva na kera na rindi, nta ho twigeze twumva inyigisho nk’izo mw’idini rya ba data mu Bakorayishi canke mu banaswara. Izo nyigisho rero, si ikindi kiretse ko ari irementanya ryigendera!"
  38,8,"Vyoshoboka gute ko Muhamadi ari we gusa muri twese yohishurirwa Qor’ani!”. Ntumwa y’Imana! Ahubwo rero abagarariji, bafise amakenga kw’ihishurirwa n’irungikwa vyawe. Ahubwo mbere binamura kuvuga ukwo, kuko batarahonja ibihano vyanje Jewe Allah."
  38,9,"Mbega none boba bagaba ibigega vy’impano z’Imana yawe Rurema Allah, Nyenintsinzi-Mutaneshwa, Bigaburo Iha uwo Ishatse mu ngabirano zayo Itarinze gusabwa!"
  38,10,"Canke boba bagaba bakaganza amajuru n’isi n’ibiri hagati yavyo, ku buryo bagaburira canke bakima uwo bashatse mu biremwa! Enda rero nibakore ibibashobokeye kugira bashike mw’ijuru, baheze rero bagaburire ibiremwa mu guha canke mu kwima uwo bashaka!"
  38,11,"Ingabo z’ababangikanyamana, zizoneshwa nk’uko ingabo ziyunze z’abo hambere yabo zaneshejwe;"
  38,12,"Aho hambere yabo, harigeze kuba hari abahakanye bivuye inyuma: abantu ba Nuhu, Bene Aadi, Firawuni yari afise ingabo n’inguvu bidasanzwe;"
  38,13,"Bene Thamuudi, abantu ba Luutwi hamwe rero n’abantu bo mu gisagara c’ibiti bitotahaye barungikiwe Shu’ayibu. Iyo migwi rero, ni yo migwi y’abantu biyunze mu bugarariji no mu buhakanyi;"
  38,14,"Umugwi wose muri yo, warahakanye wivuye inyuma Intumwa, uca uhabwa ibihano vyanje Jewe Allah."
  38,15,"Ababangikanyamana, nta n’ikindi barindiriye mu gihe boguma mw’ibangikanyamana, kiretse ivuzwa rimwe gusa ry’akaruru gahonya kadasubizwa inyuma."
  38,16,"Baranavuze batebura kw’iharurirwa ry’ibiremwa ku musi w’izuka bati: “Ewe Mana yacu Rurema Allah! Turagusavye Uduhe ibihano vyacu Watugeneye tukiri kw’isi, imbere yuko umusi w’iharurirwa ugera!”."
  38,17,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Ihanganire ivyo bavuga bikubangamiye, uheze wibuke n’Umuja wacu Dawudi yaranzwe n’inguvu zo guhangana n’abansi ata guhesha, hamwe rero no kwihanganira igamburukiramana. Mu vy’ukuri, yarigaya cane akitura kenshi Imana Allah."
  38,18,"Mu vy’ukuri Twebwe Allah, Twatumye imisozi yitabira itazira n’ininahazamana ryagirwa na Dawudi umugoroba n’igitondo;"
  38,19,"Dutuma n’umugwi w’inyoni witabira nya tazira n’ininahazamana, ivyo vyose rero vyaramwumvira;"
  38,20,"Twaranamutsimbatarije ubwami bwiwe kw’ijunja n’inguvu Twamuhaye, Tumuha n’ubutumwa hamwe no gutomora ijambo n’ingingo."
  38,21,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Mbega warashikiriwe n’inkuru y’abantu babiri batase, igihe basimba urugo rw’aho Dawudi yasengera;"
  38,22,"Baraheza bamwinjirirako aca agira ubwoba! Ni ho bamutururuza bati: “Tekana, ntugire ubwoba namba, twebwe twatase, aho umwe muri twebwe yarenganije uwundi; twaje kukwitura rero kugira udutunganirize vy’ukuri ata nkunzi, wongere uduhanure gukurikira inzira igororotseˮ."
  38,23,"Ni ho rero umwe muri bo yatangura kwigana avuga ati: “Mu vy’ukuri, uyu ni mwenewacu, afise intama mirongo icenda n’icenda, nanje nkaba mfise intama imwe rudende, akaba yagize inambu yo kuyinyaga, aca ambwira ati: “Mpa iyo ntamaˮ, maze aranzivya sinagira ayo ncira n’ayo miraˮ;"
  38,24,"Dawudi aca avuga ati: “Ni ukuri, mwenewanyu yakurenganije mu kukunyaga intama yawe akayihagira, kandi abenshi mu basangiye amatungo, ni ukuri birashika bamwe muri bo bakarenganya abandi, havuyemwo gusa abemeramana bakora ivyiza bitegetswe, ntibarenganyana. Abo rero, ni bake cane mu bantuˮ. Dawudi yaratahuye ko Twebwe Allah, Twamugerageje mu kuba abo bantu baje kumwitwarako, ni ho yasaba imbabazi Imana yiwe Rurema Allah, aca arayubamira ashira uruhanga hasi, maze arigaya;"
  38,25,"Twaciye Tumugumiriza akabanga Turanamubabarira ivyaha vyiwe. Mu vy’ukuri Dawudi, ni ukuri ari mu batonye kuri Twebwe Allah, ari no mu bagenewe uburuhukiro bwiza mu buzima bw’inyuma yo gupfa."
  38,26,"Ni ho rero Twamubwira Duti: “Ewe Dawudi! Mu vy’ukuri, Tukugize icariho cacu mu kukugira umwami kw’isi. Kubera ivyo rero, tunganiriza abantu vy’ukuri ata nkunzi, kandi ntugakurikire ivyipfuzo vyawe mu gufata ingingo, kuko vyoguhubisha inzira y’amabwirizwa y’idini ry’Imana Allah. Mu vy’ukuri abahuba inzira y’amabwirizwa y’idini ry’Imana Allah, barategekanirijwe ibihano bikaze, kuko birengagije umusi w’iharurirwa ry’ibiremwaˮ."
  38,27,"Ntitwaremye ijuru n’isi n’ibiri hagati yavyo ku gufyinata, ukwo ni ko abagararije bibwira ko Twabiremye. Ibihano nya bihano vyo mu muriro rero, vyagenewe abagarariji badategera intumbero y’Imana Allah mu kurema ijuru n’isi."
  38,28,"Mbega burya Twogira abemeye bagakora n’ivyiza bitegetswe nk’abagenzwa n’ubwononyi kw’isi, canke Twogira abagamburukiramana nk’abanyavyaha! Eka nta ho basa basana mu butoni n’ubutore ku Mana Allah."
  38,29,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Ivyo wahishuriwe, ni Igitabu gihezagiye Twakumanuriye, kugira abantu bazigame Aayah zaco baheze bazigendere, no kugira incabwenge koko zibuke zishire mu ngiro amabwirizwa y’Imana Allah."
  38,30,"Dawudi rero, Twaranamuronkeje umwana yitwa Sulayimani, yari Umuja mwiza yatewe iteka akarigendera koko; mu vy’ukuri, yarigaya cane akitura kenshi Imana Allah;"
  38,31,"Ibuka aho Sulayimani yagenzura ifarasi z’akarorero zigishijwe, agahera ku muhingamo gushika ku kirengazuba;"
  38,32,"Maze akavuga yiregura ati: “Mu vy’ukuri, jewe nahisemwo gukunda ifarasi, maze ndasamara sinibuka gutazira no kuninahaza Imana yanje Rurema Allah, gushika n’aho izuba rirenga;"
  38,33,"Ngarukanira za farasi zose nagenzuraˮ. Ni ho rero nya farasi zagarukanwa, maze azitanga ikimazi aca arazica imitsi arazikerera, kuko zatumye isengesho rimucika."
  38,34,"Ni ukuri, Twaragerageje Sulayimani, maze Dukororera ku ntebe yiwe umwana afise urubavu rumwe yavutse atageze, ni ho yagaruka ku Mana Allah arigaya;"
  38,35,"Araheza avuga mu kwigaya kwiwe ati: “Mana yanje Rurema Allah! Ngumiriza akabanga Umbabarire ivyaha, Umpe n’ubwami buhambaye Utazokwigera Uha n’umwe mu bantu bo mu nyuma zanje. Mu vy’ukuri, Wewe Uri Bigaburoˮ."
  38,36,"Ni ho rero Twamwakirira igisabisho ciwe, Tumworohereza kwikora ku muyaga, ukamwumvira mu gihe cose awutegetse kumujana aho hose ashaka;"
  38,37,"Tumworohereza no gukoresha amashetani mu bikorwa vyiwe vya misi yose; muri yo, harimwo ayubaka n’ayibira mw’ibahari;"
  38,38,"Hakaba rero n’ayandi mashetani ruhebwa yabohesha amapingu."
  38,39,"Ubu bwami buhambaye n’iyoroherezwa ryo kwikora ku muyaga no ku mashetani, ni impano yacu kuri wewe Sulayimani, uratanga utitangira, uhe uwo ushatse, wime uwo ushatse, nta wuzoguciramwo."
  38,40,"Mu vy’ukuri Sulayimani, ni ukuri ari mu batonye kuri Twebwe Allah, ari no mu bagenewe uburuhukiro bwiza mu buzima bw’inyuma yo gupfa."
  38,41,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Ibuka n’Umuja wacu Ayubu igihe yasaba gukira umuniho, atakambira Imana yiwe Rurema Allah, avuga ati: “Mu vy’ukuri shetani, yanteye umuruho n’ububabare budasanzwe buturutse ku ndwara no ku kwangara kw’umuryango wanje, hamwe rero no guhona kw’amatungo yanjeˮ;"
  38,42,"Turaheza Tubwira Ayubu Duti: “Dida ikirenge cawe hasi, haca hadudubiza amazi akanye, uheze uyanyweko wongere uyiyuhagire, indwara ice ikiraˮ."
  38,43,"Ni ho rero Twamukiza nya ndwara, Tukamutera n’iteka ryo gusubizwa abangaye mu bana no mu bagore, Tumurengerezako n’abandi nk’abo mu bana no mu buzukuru. Ivyo vyose rero, Twabigize ku mpuhwe zacu mu kumuhembera ukwihanganira igeragezwa ryamushikiye, no kugira rero bibere urwibutso incabwenge koko, ziheze zimenye ko ukwihangana gushikana umuntu ku ntsinzi."
  38,44,"Maze Tumubwira kandi Duti: “Fata umukama w’ubwatsi uwukubitishe umukenyezi wawe, mu gushira mu ngiro indahiro yawe kugira ntuyirengekoˮ. Mu vy’ukuri Twebwe Allah, Twasanze Ayubu ari umuntu yihanganira koko igeragezwa, yari n’Umuja mwiza, yatewe iteka akarigendera koko. Mu vy’ukuri, yarigaya cane akagaruka kenshi ku Mana Allah."
  38,45,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Ibuka kandi Abaja bacu: Ibrahimu, Is-haka na Yakubu, baranzwe n’ishaka n’umwete bidasanzwe kw’iyumviramana hamwe n’ubumenyi budasanzwe mw’idini;"
  38,46,"Mu vy’ukuri Twabahisemwo mu bandi, mu kubatera iteka ryo kwama bibuka gukorera ubuzima bw’inyuma yo gupfa;"
  38,47,"Mu vy’ukuri abo, ni ukuri bari mu bo Twahisemwo Tukabagira Intumwa n’intore mu kutwumvira."
  38,48,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Ongera wibuke Abaja bacu: Ismayili, Al-Yasa’a na Dhu l-Kifli, umwe wese muri bo, ni ukuri yari mu ntore zatewe iteka mu biremwa vy’Imana Allah."
  38,49,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Iyi Qor’ani, ni iteka n’urwibutso kuri wewe no ku bantu bawe warungitsweko. Mu vy’ukuri abagamburukiramana, ni ukuri baragenewe uburuhukiro bwiza;"
  38,50,"Ubwo buruhukiro bukaba ari imirima itotahaye yo mu Bwami bw’ijuru rya “Adeni” bazokwugururirwa imiryango yabwo;"
  38,51,"Aho bazoba bicaye ku nyegamo zisharije, basaba guherezwa ivyo bipfuza mu vyamwa vy’ubwoko bwinshi hamwe n’ibinyobwa bitandukanye;"
  38,52,"Muri nya Bwami, bazoba bafise n’abakenyezi bagumiza akajisho ku bagabo babo, bari mu runganwe rumwe n’urugero rumwe."
  38,53,"Bagamburukiramana! Izo nema rero, ziri mu vyo musezeraniwe kuzoronka ku musi w’iharurirwa ry’ibiremwa;"
  38,54,"Mu vy’ukuri, izo ni zo mpano zacu kuri mwebwe, ntizigera zishira canke ngo zikehe;"
  38,55,"Izo rero, ni zo mpano zagenewe abagamburukiramana. Nayo abimonogoje mu bugarariji, ni ukuri bagenewe uburuhukiro bubi cane;"
  38,56,"Ubwo buruhukiro bukaba ari umuriro wa Jahannamu, bazokwinjira maze bakawota. Ubwo rero, ni bwo busaswa bubi cane bubaho;"
  38,57,"Ibi, ni vyo bihano bazohonja; ukunywa amazi asebuye akaryimara, urwuya hamwe n’amashira bitemba biva mu mibiri y’abantu bo mu muriro udahera;"
  38,58,"Bazohabwa n’ibindi bihano rero nk’ivyo vy’ubwoko bwose."
  38,59,"Igihe abimonogoje mu bugarariji binjiye mu muriro, bazotanako umwikomo, maze babwirane hagati yabo bati: “Ng’uwo umugwi w’abantu isinzi, utegerezwa kwinjirana na mwe mu muriro udaheraˮ. Abari muri uwo muriro bazobishura bati: “Ntibagahabwe ikaze, ntibakagire uburaro n’uburamuko mu muriro, ni ukuri nibinjire mu muriro baheze bawote nkatweˮ;"
  38,60,"Abumviye abimonogoje mu bugarariji bakabakurikira, bazosubizayo bati: “Ahubwo mwebwe nyabuna ntimugahabwe ikaze, kuko ari mwebwe mwaduhubishije kw’isi mugatuma twinjira muri woˮ. Umuriro udahera rero, ni bwo buraro n’uburamuko bubi cane bubaho;"
  38,61,"Abumviye abimonogoje mu bugarariji, bazobandanya basabira ababahubishije, ko bohanwa vy’akarorero bati: “Mana yacu Rurema Allah! Abaduhubishije inzira yawe kw’isi, turagusavye ubongerereze ibihano ku bindi mu muriro udaheraˮ."
  38,62,"Abimonogoje mu bugarariji na bo, bazovuga bitangaza bati: “Mbega vyagenze gute ko mu muriro tutabonayo abantu twahora duharura kw’isi ko bari mu banyavyaha!"
  38,63,"Mbega twoba twarabihenzeko mu kubateburako tubasuzugura, canke twoba tudashoboye gusa kubabona kandi bari kumwe na twe mu muriro!ˮ."
  38,64,"Iryo tanako ry’umwikomo hagati y’abantu bo mu muriro, nta nkeka ko ari iry’ukuri kandi rizoshika."
  38,65,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Bwira abantu bawe warungitsweko uti: “Ni ukuri jewe, ndi Umugabisha kuri mwebwe ku bihano vy’Imana Allah, nta mana ibwirijwe gusengwa vy’ukuri atari Imana Allah Nyarudende, Nyeninkomezi-ntangere;"
  38,66,"Ni Yo Mana Rurema Ikaba n’Umubungabunzi w’amajuru n’isi n’ibiri hagati yavyo, Nyenintsinzi-Mutaneshwa, Nyenimbabazinyinshiˮ."
  38,67,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Bwira abantu bawe warungitsweko uti: “Iyi Qor’ani, ni inkuru ihambaye, ngirakamaro cane;"
  38,68,"Mwebwe mwirengagiza kuyitegera no kuyigendera;"
  38,69,"Nta bumenyi nogira ku vyerekeye uruhara rw’abamalayika kw’iremwa rya Adamu, kiretse ivyo nahishuriwe n’Imana Allah;"
  38,70,"Nta co Impishurira ngo menye ivyo ntari nzi, atari uko ndi Umugabisha ku bihano vyayo, ntomora amabwirizwa yayoˮ."
  38,71,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Ibutsa abo warungitsweko, igihe Imana yawe Rurema Allah Yabwira abamalayika Iti: “Mu vy’ukuri, Jewe Ngira Ndeme umuntu mw’ivu;"
  38,72,"Ninamara gutunganya indemo y’umubiri wiwe, nkamuhuhiramwo n’inkomoko y’ubuzima “Roho” akaba muzima, muraheza rero mumuhe icubahiro kimukwiye mu kumwubamira”."
  38,73,"Abamalayika baraheza baragamburuka bose barubama;"
  38,74,"Kiretse Ibilisi, yanse n’amanyama n’akantu kumwubamira, gutyo aca aba mu bagarariji;"
  38,75,"Imana Allah Iraheza Ibaza Ibilisi icatumye atubama Iti: “Ewe Ibilisi! Ni igiki cakubujije kwubamira ikiremwa Niremeye n’amaboko yanje! Wabigize ku manyama n’agasuzuguro, canke uri mu bihambaza ku Mana yawe Rurema!”."
  38,76,"Ibilisi yishuye n’amanyama n’akantu ati: “Sinubamiye ico kiremwa kuko jewe ndi intore kugisumba, Wandemye mu rubeya rw’umuriro, na co Ukirema mw’ivu!”."
  38,77,"Imana Allah, Iraheza Ibwira Ibilisi Iti: “Kubera ivyo rero, va mu Bwami bw’ijuru, kuko wewe mu vy’ukuri uravumwe;"
  38,78,"Ni ukuri uzobaho mw’ivumwe ryanje, gushika ku musi w’iharurirwa n’impera”."
  38,79,"Ibilisi abonye ko kabaye, yavuze ati: “Mana yanje Rurema Allah! Ndagusavye Umpe kuramba gushika ku musi w’izuka ry’ibiremwa”."
  38,80,"Imana Allah Iraheza Imwishura Iti: “Mu vy’ukuri, wewe uri mu bazoramba;"
  38,81,"Gushika ku musi w’isango nyezina, rizwi ryo guhonya ibiremwa vyose”."
  38,82,"Ni ho Ibilisi yavuga n’agahigihigi n’akantu ati: “Ndarahiye ku cubahiro c’iteka ryawe, ni ukuri ntegerezwa guhubisha Bene Adamu;"
  38,83,"Kiretse gusa abo Wejeje mu baja bawe, Ukabaha ubudahangarwa, ku buryo ata nzira n’imwe yo kubahubisha noronka ncamwo”."
  38,84,"Imana Allah Yavuze Iti: “Uku ni ukuri kuvuye kuri Jewe Allah, kanatsinda sinigera Mvuga atari ukuri;"
  38,85,"Ni ukuri Nzokwuzuza mu muriro wa Jahannamu, uruvyaro rugukomokako hamwe n’abazogukurikira bose muri Bene Adamu”."
  38,86,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Bwira ababangikanyamana uti: “Nta mpembo ndabasavye kw’ishikirizabutumwa ryanje, eka si ndi no mu barementanya bihatira gushikiriza ivyo batahishuriwe”."
  38,87,"Iyi Qor’ani rero, si ikindi kiretse ko ari urwibutso ku biremwa; abantu n’amajini kugira vyikebuke mu gukora ivyobigirira akamaro mu buzima bwo kw’isi no mu bw’inyuma yo gupfa."
  38,88,"Babangikanyamana! Ni ukuri muzomenya ukuri kw’inkuru ya Qor’ani igihe ubwislamu bwatsinze, maze abantu bakabwinjiramwo ari imigwimigwi; n’igihe rero mwahaniwe kuyigarariza, ata wuronka ayo acira n’ayo amira."
